3ï¸âƒ£ Usability Testing (MOST IMPORTANT)
What is Uability Testing?
Usability testing checks:
How easy and comfortable the software is for users.

It answers:
Is it easy to use?
Is navigation clear?
Can a normal user understand it?

ğŸ§  Key Line:
Usability testing focuses on user experience, not just functionality.

Why Usability Testing Matters?
Users leave confusing apps
Poor UX = business loss
Good usability = user retention
